        Parameters:
        id - - Item ID
        sourceId - - Foreign Key pointing to source record
        name - - Name of the item being sold
        description - - description of the item
        platform - - platform the item is being sold on
        purchasePrice - - Price paid for the item
        listedPrice - - Price the item is listed for
        salePrice - - price the item was sold for
        shippingCost - - Cost seller paid for shipping
        fee - - fee the seller paid to the platform
        purchaseDate - - Date item was purchased
        salesDate - - Date item was sold
